the aspern papers is a novella written by henry james , originally published in the atlantic monthly in 1888 , with its first book publication later in the same year .

literary venice : ( jimmy of the clue crew reports from caffe florian in venice , italy . )   i 'm at caffe florian , a favorite spot of this u.s.-born author , who wrote about it in " the wings of the dove " and " the aspern papers "

